OL,3,CFox who stowed away on ship from UK to
OL,4,CNew York 'settling in well' at Bronx
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FA stowaway fox who took a
OL,8,Ftransatlantic trip to New York after
OL,9,Fslipping onto a cargo ship from
OL,10,FSouthampton is "settling in well" to
OL,11,Fhis new home at the Bronx Zoo.
OL,13,FThe zoo said the 11-pound (5-kilogram)
OL,14,Fmale fox, who is thought to be about
OL,15,Ftwo years old, appears healthy after
OL,16,Fearly examinations.
OL,18,F"He seems to be settling in well,"
OL,19,FKeith Lovett, the zoo's director of
OL,20,Fanimal programs, adding: "It's gone
OL,21,Fthrough a lot."
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@bO]|D@ZOU}D@OO]
