OL,3,CFox who stowed away on ship from UK to
OL,4,CNew York 'settling in well' at Bronx
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FThe ship loaded with cars left
OL,8,FSouthampton on February 4, according
OL,9,Fto the zoo, arriving in February 18 at
OL,10,Fthe Port of New York and New Jersey.
