OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773349566
OL,3,CFox who stowed away on ship from UK to
OL,4,CNew York 'settling in well' at Bronx
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FThe species, formally named Vulpes
OL,8,Fvulpes, is widespread in Europe, Asia,
OL,9,FNorth America and parts of Africa. A
OL,10,Flong-term home for this fox will be
OL,11,Ffound once he clears some more health
OL,12,Fscreening.
OL,14,FHe is currently being cared for at the
OL,15,Fzoo's veterinary centre, where he is
OL,16,Fenjoying a diet of proteins and some
OL,17,Fbiscuit-like items.
